All event-level decisions are made on top of 60-s windows with 75% overlap (15-s stride). For each recording, we apply a centered moving average over 3 consecutive window scores (kernel size = 3 windows at 15-s stride). The smoothed sequence is then thresholded at \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
